data.description: Step into your new home, a spacious 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom haven with beautiful tile flooring throughout. The kitchen boasts a stylish island and sleek white cabinetry, making it a perfect space for cooking and entertaining. Outside, you'll find a charming patio where you can relax and enjoy the fresh air. The fenced yard adds privacy and security, and there's even a convenient shed for extra storage. Located in a friendly neighborhood with no HOA fees, this home offers both comfort and freedom. Don't miss the chance to make this house your home!
